# Planning Index

## Overview
Forward-looking planning and roadmap for The Kepler Testimonies development.

## Current Status
Premise selected. Story development not yet begun.

## Immediate Next Steps
1. Expand the premise into a story concept
2. Develop the world/setting (the Kepler, its mission, its crew)
3. Design the testimony structure (how 500 testimonies are organized)
4. Identify the 12 "impossible" testimonies and what makes them impossible
5. Establish community voting process for major decisions

## Future Phases (Not Yet Planned)
- Character development
- Plot outlining
- Drafting process
- Revision process
- Publication/release

